{"tid":710814,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"好擔心自己健康不再","createTime":"2018-06-21T05:08:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T07:12:59.000Z","uid":167330,"like":63,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e805f5f623a3a10f97c85125706a198d7f660e3f","tid":710814,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T05:08:44.000Z","msg":"我係上個禮拜因爲心跳跳到二百幾入咗icu嗰位巴打，經過一個禮拜，琴晚終於返咗屋企。<br />\n<br />\n但我發現自己心跳始終返唔到以前咁，點都係偏高。我以往都算係會做下運動嘅人嚟，會起屋企做下gym，耐唔耐出去跑下步咁，而做gym嗰陣心跳只會係11X，跑步停低之後心跳都會即刻回落到11X，但我而家坐起到心跳都100，企起到心跳就11X-120左右，琴晚沖涼嗰陣心跳就已經130。前提係我已經有食緊減慢心跳嘅藥。<br />\n<br />\n我好擔心自己以後都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我先19歲，retake一年，過幾個月就上大專，如果我繼續係咁嘅情況，真係怕以後乜野都唔駛做，咩ocamp、上莊......最怕就係連運動都做唔到，因為咁樣身體只會越嚟越差。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 起到奉勸各位巴絲打，唔好因爲年輕就不斷剝削自己嘅身體。你年輕，有本錢，可以任意揮霍，但筆債遲早需要還，趁仲未有機會俾你後悔，就好好珍惜自己嘅健康，一日仲有健康，就仲有機會拼搏，唔好為咗一時，chur盡晒自己嘅本錢</span><br />\n<br />\n我曾經都以為自己起碼過多幾十年先會有咩病，但到咗而家落地都覺得腳軟，先至後悔以前長期夜瞓、運動做得唔夠......<br />\n<br />\n改善咗生活習慣，未必一定改善到健康，但最起碼有一日你唔好彩病咗嘅時候，你俾唔到籍口自己後悔先。<br />\n<br />\n起到呻下，希望自己好得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ca54446ad3dfbc29a4a7186a5f4d67e0cfb20a","tid":710814,"uid":39428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T05:10:39.000Z","msg":"人越大真係覺得健康好緊要"},{"pid":"7b6f369b59cd2eebc029e3840ddeac9560c0650c","tid":710814,"uid":18411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T05:12:52.000Z","msg":"ching做過咩事？<br />\n點解十九歲會搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6f45e372d1501e1d7c415b843a91bc225789133","tid":710814,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b6f369b59cd2eebc029e3840ddeac9560c0650c","tid":710814,"uid":18411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T05:12:52.000Z","msg":"ching做過咩事？<br />\n點解十九歲會搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T05:17:36.000Z","msg":"我冇做過咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，都係夜瞓嗰啲啫，但我起到諗如果以前有跑多啲步，個心強啲嘅話未必會搞到游完水之心臟病"},{"pid":"cdee15440d21038a723cf35283e0ce39bd5622f9","tid":710814,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T05:47:00.000Z","msg":"我推<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/134659_ea624ac5efa38722a30ffa8a66f453f5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F134659_ea624ac5efa38722a30ffa8a66f453f5.gif&h=30f0ad7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34c5b1f56c27b0f18ee5f57b27df9228f29841fa","tid":710814,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T05:49:27.000Z","msg":"垃圾基因<br />\n<br />\n我每日訓三個鐘就好撚精神 <br />\n<br />\n自然醒個隻"},{"pid":"d0147a63bda50fbcc2a2c062352c1f18496c348a","tid":710814,"uid":57410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"34c5b1f56c27b0f18ee5f57b27df9228f29841fa","tid":710814,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T05:49:27.000Z","msg":"垃圾基因<br />\n<br />\n我每日訓三個鐘就好撚精神 <br />\n<br />\n自然醒個隻"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T05:51:19.000Z","msg":"你叻呀你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c28b8531ed8a8acb5578a3254efdeae3afcd49","tid":710814,"uid":24519,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"d0147a63bda50fbcc2a2c062352c1f18496c348a","tid":710814,"uid":57410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"34c5b1f56c27b0f18ee5f57b27df9228f29841fa","tid":710814,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T05:49:27.000Z","msg":"垃圾基因<br />\n<br />\n我每日訓三個鐘就好撚精神 <br />\n<br />\n自然醒個隻"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T05:51:19.000Z","msg":"你叻呀你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T05:58:07.000Z","msg":"俾佢威多幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fa